  "prompt": "Who is Bruce Wayne?",
  "response": "Bruce Wayne is a fictional character from DC Comics, best known as the alter ego of Batman. He is a wealthy industrialist and philanthropist who resides in Gotham City. After witnessing the murder of his parents as a child, Bruce dedicates his life to fighting crime and injustice. He uses his wealth to develop advanced technology and gadgets, and he undergoes rigorous physical and mental training to become a skilled martial artist and detective. As Batman, he operates at night, often working alone or alongside allies such as Robin, Batgirl, and the Justice League to combat various villains, including the Joker, Catwoman, and the Penguin. Bruce Wayne's character explores themes of vengeance, justice, and the psychological impact of trauma.",
